Summary: Properties of the CompressedTexture2D class including load path and resource localization settings.

Properties:
- String: load_path (overrides Resource.load_path). Default: "".
- bool: resource_local_to_scene. Default: false (overrides Resource.resource_local_to_scene). Note: This setting takes precedence over the base Resource class's equivalent property.
